#.python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if delegates have different OS, they may choose to ignore it.
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipenv, poetry.lock contains exact versions, but can be ignored if preferred.
#poetry.lock

